Little-Known Investment Gets Money Flowing in like Niagara Falls

There's a group of investments you've probably never heard of that are
making some Americans very rich.

They're called income trusts, and they give you the most gratifying return
you can imagine -- cash now.  Annual yields often run into double digits.

Recently, the government imposed strict new rules on income trusts but
left a select group of trusts untouched until 2011.

This select group of trusts will get richer and richer over the next four
years as the trust market shakes out.

That means you have four more years to reap spectacular profits from these
cash-rich trusts. But you need clear, specific advice to profit fully from
